# ── LLM Configuration ──────────────────────────────────────────────

# Just set MODEL and API_KEY below.  Change both whenever you switch providers.

# Format: 
# provider/model-id  (CrewAI / LiteLLM format)
# API_KEY=your_api_key_here (provided by your LLM provider, if required)

# Examples:
#   MODEL=groq/llama-3.1-70b-versatile   API_KEY=gsk_...       (FREE)
#   MODEL=gemini/gemini-2.5-pro           API_KEY=AIza...       (FREE tier)
#   MODEL=openai/gpt-4o                   API_KEY=sk-...        (paid)
#   MODEL=anthropic/claude-3-5-sonnet-20241022  API_KEY=sk-ant-...  (paid)
#   MODEL=ollama/llama3.2                 API_KEY=               (local, no key needed)

